{"main":["switch.js","switch.css"],"options":[{"name":"collapse","type":"boolean","default":"true","description":"Allow switch to collapse it's target"},{"name":"maxWidth","type":"string","default":"Infinity","description":"Width at which to auto-disable plugin"}],"events":[{"name":"activate.switch","description":"Switch activated"},{"name":"deactivate.switch","description":"Switch deactivated"},{"name":"enable.switch","description":"Switch enabled"},{"name":"disable.switch","description":"Switch diabled"}],"methods":[{"name":"activate","description":"Activate instance.","example":"$(\".target\").switch(\"activate\");"},{"name":"deactivate","description":"Deactivates instance.","example":"$(\".target\").switch(\"deactivate\");"},{"name":"defaults","description":"Extends plugin default settings; effects instances created hereafter.","params":[{"name":"options","type":"object","default":"{}","description":"New plugin defaults"}],"example":"$.switch(\"defaults\", { ... });"},{"name":"destroy","description":"Removes plugin instance.","example":"$(\".target\").switch(\"destroy\");"},{"name":"disable","description":"Disables instance.","example":"$(\".target\").switch(\"disable\");"},{"name":"enable","description":"Enables instance.","example":"$(\".target\").switch(\"enable\");"}],"name":"Switch","type":"widget","description":"A jQuery plugin for toggling states.","dependencies":["core.js","mediaquery.js","touch.js"],"css":[{"name":".fs-switch-element","type":"element","description":"Target Element"},{"name":".fs-switch-target","type":"element","description":"Toggled element"},{"name":".fs-switch-enabled","type":"modifier","description":"Indicates enabled state"},{"name":".fs-switch-active","type":"modifier","description":"Indicates active state"}],"use":"### Basic\n\nSwitch toggles classes on groups of elements based on configuration options and user interaction. It is up to the developer to utilize the classes.\n\n```javascript\n$(\".target\").switch();\n```\n\n```markup\n<div class=\"target\" data-switch-target=\".toggle\">Toggle</div>\n<div class=\"toggle\">Target</div>\n```\n\n### Groups\n\nSwitches can be grouped together for a simple accordions or tabs.\n\n```markup\n<h4>Grouped</h4>\n<div class=\"target\" data-switch-target=\".toggle_1\" data-switch-group=\"group_1\">Toggle - 1</div>\n<div class=\"target\" data-switch-target=\".toggle_2\" data-switch-group=\"group_1\">Toggle - 2</div>\n\n<div class=\"toggle_1\">Target - 1</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_2\">Target - 2</div>\n```\n\n### Max Width\n\nSwitches will auto-enable and disable themselves if the `maxWidth` property is set.\n\n```javascript\n$(\".target\").switch({\n\tmaxWidth: \"740px\"\n});\n```\n\n```markup\n<div class=\"target\" data-switch-target=\".toggle\">Toggle</div>\n<div class=\"switch\">Target</div>\n```\n","demo":"<style>\n\t.toggle.fs-switch-enabled { color: #393b3f; }\n\t.toggle.fs-switch-active { color: #c65032; }\n\n\t.toggle_target { background: #c65032; border-radius: 3px; color: #fff; height: 50px; line-height: 50px; margin: 10px 0; text-align: center; width: 100%; }\n\t.toggle_target.fs-switch-enabled.fs-switch-target { display: none; }\n\t.toggle_target.fs-switch-enabled.fs-switch-active { display: block; }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n\t$(function() {\n\t\t$(\".toggle\").switch();\n\t});\n</script>\n\n<h4>Basic</h4>\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_0\">Toggle</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_0\">Target</div>\n\n<h4>Grouped</h4>\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_1\" data-switch-group=\"toggle_group_1\">Toggle 1</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_1\">Target 1</div>\n\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_2\" data-switch-group=\"toggle_group_1\">Toggle 2</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_2\">Target 2</div>\n\n<h4>Grouped (no collapse)</h4>\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-active=\"true\" data-switch-options='{\"collapse\":false}' data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_3\" data-switch-group=\"toggle_group_2\">Toggle 1</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_3\">Target 1</div>\n\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-options='{\"collapse\":false}' data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_4\" data-switch-group=\"toggle_group_2\">Toggle 2</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_4\">Target 2</div>\n\n<h4>Max Width</h4>\n<div class=\"toggle\" data-switch-options='{\"maxWidth\":\"740px\"}' data-switch-target=\".toggle_target_5\">Toggle</div>\n<div class=\"toggle_target toggle_target_5\">Target</div>"}